result.execSummary:
The defendant Lorraine Madaline Holden was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Lorraine Madaline Holden is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Lorraine Madaline Holden was found guilty of Possession of Cocaine/Coca(2nd+), a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(c).
